###################################################################
# Triggered modifiers are here.
# these are checked for each countries once/month and then applied.
#
# Effects are fully scriptable here.
###################################################################

minimal_training_active_I = {
	potential = {
		check_variable = {
			which = "minimal_training_days_active"
			value = 1
		}
		not = {
			check_variable = {
				which = "minimal_training_days_active"
				value = 180
			}
		}
	}
	trigger = {
		check_variable = {
			which = "minimal_training_days_active"
			value = 30
		}
		not = {
			check_variable = {
				which = "minimal_training_days_active"
				value = 180
			}
		}
	}
	land_organisation = -0.05
	air_organisation = -0.05
	naval_organisation = -0.05
	org_regain = -0.05
}
minimal_training_active_II = {
	potential = {
		check_variable = {
			which = "minimal_training_days_active"
			value = 30
		}
		not = {
			check_variable = {
				which = "minimal_training_days_active"
				value = 360
			}
		}
	}
	trigger = {
		check_variable = {
			which = "minimal_training_days_active"
			value = 180
		}
		not = {
			check_variable = {
				which = "minimal_training_days_active"
				value = 360
			}
		}
	}
	land_organisation = -0.1
	air_organisation = -0.1
	naval_organisation = -0.1
	org_regain = -0.1
}

		}
	}
	land_organisation = -0.15

	naval_organisation = -0.15
	org_regain = -0.15
}

		}
		not = {

				value = 180
			}
		}
	}
	unit_start_experience = 3
}

Stalin_HOG_effect_AI = {
	potential = {
		tag = SOV
		head_of_government = 4002
		industrial_policy_laws = heavy_industry_emphasis
		not = { war_with = GER }
		#ai = yes
	}
	trigger = {
		tag = SOV
		head_of_government = 4002
		industrial_policy_laws = heavy_industry_emphasis
		not = { war_with = GER }
		ai = yes
	}

	#peace_consumer_goods_demand = -1.0

	icon = 84
}
SOV_AI_BALANCE = {
	potential = {
		tag = SOV
		ai = yes
	}
	trigger = {}

	#unit_repair = 0.5
	supply_consumption = -0.5
	supply_throughput = 1
	#land_organisation = -0.55

	icon = 5
}
SOV_AI_TWEAK = {
	potential = {
		tag = SOV
		#ai = yes
	}
	trigger = {
		#GER = {
		#	ai = yes
		#}
		#not = {
		#	year = 1944
		#}
		not = {
			war_with = JAP
		}
		
		or = {
			and = {
				#war_with = GER
				total_amount_of_brigades = 5000
				PER = {
					faction = axis
				}
				TUR = {
					faction = axis
				}
			}
			and = {
				#war_with = GER
				total_amount_of_brigades = 4500
				or = {
					and = {
						PER = {
							faction = axis
						}
						not = {
							TUR = {
								faction = axis
							}
						}
					}
					and = {
						TUR = {
							faction = axis
						}
						not = {
							PER = {
								faction = axis
							}
						}
					}
					and = {
						not = {
							exists = PER
						}
						TUR = {
							faction = axis
						}
					}
				}
			}
			and = {
				#war_with = GER
				total_amount_of_brigades = 4100
				or = {
					not = {
						PER = {
							faction = axis
						}
					}
					not = {
						exists = PER
					}
				}
				not = {
					TUR = {
						faction = axis
					}
				}
			}
		}
	}

	land_build_speed = 5
	tank_build_speed = 5
	#air_build_speed = 0.65

	icon = 5
}
SOV_AI_WAR_I = {
	potential = {
		tag = SOV
		ai = yes
	}
	trigger = {
		or = {
			and = {
				war_with = GER
				not = {
					war_with = JAP
				}
				not = {
					total_amount_of_brigades = 2000
				}
			}
			and = {
				war_with = GER
				war_with = JAP
				not = {
					total_amount_of_brigades = 3000
				}
			}
		}
	}

	land_build_speed = -1.75
	tank_build_speed = -1.75

	icon = 5
}
SOV_AI_WAR_II = {
	potential = {
		tag = SOV
		ai = yes
	}
	trigger = {
		or = {
			and = {
				war_with = GER
				not = {
					war_with = JAP
				}
				not = {
					total_amount_of_brigades = 3000
				}
				total_amount_of_brigades = 2000
			}
			and = {
				war_with = GER
				war_with = JAP
				not = {
					total_amount_of_brigades = 4000
				}
				total_amount_of_brigades = 3000
			}
		}
	}

	land_build_speed = -1.25
	tank_build_speed = -1.25

	icon = 5
}
SOV_AI_WAR_III = {
	potential = {
		tag = SOV
		ai = yes
	}
	trigger = {
		war_with = GER
		or = {
			and = {
				war_with = GER
				not = {
					war_with = JAP
				}
				not = {
					total_amount_of_brigades = 4000
				}
				total_amount_of_brigades = 3000
			}
			and = {
				war_with = GER
				war_with = JAP
				not = {
					total_amount_of_brigades = 5000
				}
				total_amount_of_brigades = 4000
			}
		}
	}

	land_build_speed = -0.75
	tank_build_speed = -0.75

	icon = 5
}

Blitz_effect = {
	potential = {
		tag = GER
		2613 = {
			controller = {
				faction = axis
			}
		}
	}
	trigger = {
		has_country_modifier = Paying_for_the_Blitz
	}

	strategic_attack = 0.15
	air_intercept = 0.1
	air_organisation = 0.1

	global_ic = -0.05
	global_money = -0.05
	global_supplies = -0.05

	icon = 7
}

Nat_focus_ground_forces_start = {
	potential = {
		check_variable = {
			which = "ground_forces_national_focus_days_active"
			value = 1
		}
		not = {
			check_variable = {
				which = "ground_forces_national_focus_days_active"
				value = 90
			}
		}
	}
	trigger = {
		check_variable = {
			which = "ground_forces_national_focus_days_active"
			value = 1
		}
		not = {
			check_variable = {
				which = "ground_forces_national_focus_days_active"
				value = 90
			}
		}
	}

	icon = 5
}

}

###########################################################
###############		 WAR EXHAUSTION 	 	###############
###########################################################

WE_low = {
	potential = {
		check_variable = {
			which = "war_exhaustion"
			value = 1
		}
	}
	trigger = {
		check_variable = {
			which = "war_exhaustion"
			value = 2500
		}
		not = {
			check_variable = {
				which = "war_exhaustion"
				value = 6500
			}
		}
	}

	ruling_party_support = -0.05
	national_unity = -0.025
	global_manpower_modifier = -0.1

	icon = 5
}
WE_medium = {
	potential = {
		check_variable = {
			which = "war_exhaustion"
			value = 5500
		}
		not = {
			check_variable = {
				which = "war_exhaustion"
				value = 7500
			}
		}
	}
	trigger = {
		check_variable = {
			which = "war_exhaustion"
			value = 6500
		}
		not = {
			check_variable = {
				which = "war_exhaustion"
				value = 9500
			}
		}
	}

	ruling_party_support = -0.1
	national_unity = -0.05
	global_manpower_modifier = -0.2
	global_revolt_risk = 2

	icon = 5
}
WE_high = {
	potential = {
		check_variable = {
			which = "war_exhaustion"
			value = 8500
		}
		not = {
			check_variable = {
				which = "war_exhaustion"
				value = 11000
			}
		}
	}
	trigger = {
		or = {
			and = {
				war = yes
				check_variable = {
					which = "war_exhaustion"
					value = 9500
				}
				not = {
					check_variable = {
						which = "war_exhaustion"
						value = 11000
					}
				}
			}
			and = {
				war = no
				check_variable = {
					which = "war_exhaustion"
					value = 9500
				}
			}
		}
	}

	ruling_party_support = -0.15
	national_unity = -0.1
	global_manpower_modifier = -0.3
	global_revolt_risk = 4


	icon = 5
}
WE_extreme = {
	potential = {
		war = yes
		check_variable = {
			which = "war_exhaustion"
			value = 9500
		}
	}
	trigger = {
		check_variable = {
			which = "war_exhaustion"
			value = 11000
		}
	}

	ruling_party_support = -0.25
	national_unity = -0.15
	global_manpower_modifier = -0.45
	global_revolt_risk = 6

	icon = 5
}

###############################################################
###############		event unit IC penalty		###############
###############################################################


### 20% ###
ic_investment_II = {
	potential = {
		ai = no
		check_variable = {
			which = IC_days_spent
			value = 1
		}
		check_variable = {
			which = event_unit_investment
			value = 20
		}
		not = {
			check_variable = {
				which = event_unit_investment
				value = 21
			}
		}
	}
	trigger = {
		check_variable = {
			which = IC_days_spent
			value = 1
		}
	}

	global_ic = -0.2
}

### 30% ###

			}
		}
	}

		check_variable = {

			value = 1
		}
	}

	global_ic = -0.3
}

ic_investment_VI = {
	potential = {
		ai = no
		check_variable = {
			which = IC_days_spent
			value = 1
		}
		check_variable = {
			which = event_unit_investment
			value = 60
		}
		not = {
			check_variable = {
				which = event_unit_investment
				value = 61
			}
		}
	}
	trigger = {
		check_variable = {
			which = IC_days_spent
			value = 1
		}
	}

	global_ic = -0.6
}

### Penalty for being 20000 IC days in debt ###
ic_investment_debt_twenty = {
	potential = {
		ai = no
		check_variable = {
			which = IC_days_spent
			value = 10000
		}
	}
	trigger = {
		check_variable = {
			which = IC_days_spent
			value = 20000
		}
	}
	org_regain = -0.05
	land_organisation = -0.05
	air_organisation = -0.05
	soft_attack = -0.05
	hard_attack = -0.05
}

		not = { total_amount_of_ships = 50 }
	}

		total_amount_of_ships = 50
	}

	global_crude_oil = -0.05

	icon = 16

}

## Neutrality
neutrality = {

	potential = {
		not = {
			or = {
				faction = allies
				faction = axis
				faction = comintern
			}
			tag = USA
		}
	}

	trigger = {
		not = {
			or = {
				faction = allies
				faction = axis
				faction = comintern
				war = yes
			}
		}
	}

	officer_recruitment = -0.25
	#global_manpower_modifier = -0.25
	land_build_speed = 0.02
	tank_build_speed = 0.02
	air_build_speed = 0.02
	naval_build_speed = 0.02
	counter_espionage = 0.1

	icon = 14
}

## General Winter

		not =  {has_global_flag = NO_MODIFIERS }
		tag = SOV
		has_country_modifier = patriotic_war
	}

	trigger = {
		tag = SOV
		war_with = GER

			or = {
				controls = 1534
				controls = 2223
				controls = 1991
				controls = 3175
				controls = 1535
				controls = 1182
				controls = 1102
				controls = 909
				controls = 782
			}
		}
		or = {
			month = 11
			not = {
				month = 3
			}
		}
	}

	org_regain = 0.25
	territorial_pride = 0.05
	#defence_modifier = 0.6
	#offence_modifier = 0.2
	#reinforcement_bonus = 0.5

	icon = 8
}

# desperate_defence
desperate_defence = {

	potential = {
		not =  {has_global_flag = NO_MODIFIERS }
		tag = CHI
		JAP = { ai = yes }
	}

	trigger = {
		not = { controls = 4685 }
		not = { controls = 5020 }
		not = { controls = 5182 }
		not = { controls = 5341 }
		not = { controls = 7139 }
		war_with = JAP
	}

	#territorial_pride = 0.05
	org_regain = 0.025
	land_organisation = -0.25
	global_leadership_modifier = -0.3

	icon = 5
}

	potential = {
		not =  { has_global_flag = NO_MODIFIERS }
		tag = CHC
		not = { controls = 4685 }
		not = { controls = 5020 }
		not = { controls = 5182 }
		not = { controls = 5341 }
		not = { controls = 7139 }
		JAP = { ai = yes }
	}

	trigger = {
		war_with = JAP
	}

	#territorial_pride = 0.05
	org_regain = 0.05
	land_organisation = -0.3
	global_leadership_modifier = -0.3

	icon = 5
}

# military crisis
military_crisis_I = {

	potential = {
		not =  { has_global_flag = NO_MODIFIERS }
		or = {
			GER = { war_with = SOV }
			not = { year = 1942 }
		}
		tag = HOL
		GER = { has_country_flag = fr_goal_nag_no }
	}

	trigger = {
		war_with = GER
	}

	land_organisation = -0.40
	org_regain = -0.3
	#industrial_efficiency = -0.5
	#global_leadership_modifier = -0.3

	icon = 5
}
military_crisis_II = {

	potential = {
		tag = FRA
		or = {
			GER = { war_with = SOV }
			not = { year = 1942 }
		}
	}

	trigger = {
		war_with = GER
		and = {
			not = { GER = { war_with = SOV } }
			not = { year = 1942 }
		}
		or = {
			not = { has_global_flag = UKvhard }
			not = { has_global_flag = UKhard }
		}
	}

	land_organisation = -0.45
	org_regain = -0.45
	#industrial_efficiency = -0.5
	global_leadership_modifier = -0.3

	icon = 5
}
military_crisis_III = {

	potential = {
		tag = BEL
		or = {
		GER = { war_with = SOV }
		not = { year = 1942 }
		}
		GER = { has_country_flag = fr_goal_nag_no }
		not =  { has_global_flag = NO_MODIFIERS }
	}

	trigger = {
		war_with = GER
	}

	land_organisation = -0.35
	org_regain = -0.25

	icon = 5
}

### SPANISH CIVIL WAR ENDER ##
madrid_loss_SPA = { #Capital Loss

	potential = {
		tag = SPA
		exists = SPR
		war_with = SPR
		year = 1939
		ai = yes
	}

	trigger = {
		or = {
			not = { 4540 = { controlled_by = SPA } } #Madrid
			and = {
				not = { 4218 = { controlled_by = SPA } } #Valladolid
				not = { 4347 = { controlled_by = SPA } } #Salamanca
			}
		}
	}

	land_organisation = -0.20
	air_organisation = -0.20
	naval_organisation = -0.20
	org_regain = -0.20
	territorial_pride = -0.15
	ruling_party_support = -0.25

	icon = 5
}

	potential = {
		tag = SPR
		exists = SPA
		war_with = SPA
		year = 1939
		ai = yes
	}

	trigger = {
		or = {
			not = { 4540 = { controlled_by = SPR } } #Madrid
			and = {
				not = { 4548 = { controlled_by = SPR } } #Barcelona
				not = { 4862 = { controlled_by = SPR } } #Valencia
			}
		}
	}

	land_organisation = -0.20
	air_organisation = -0.20
	naval_organisation = -0.20
	org_regain = -0.20
	territorial_pride = -0.15
	ruling_party_support = -0.25

	icon = 5
}

				tag = SPR

				}
			not = { year = 1941 }
			ai = no
		}
	}
	trigger = {

		war_with = SPR

		}
	}

	war_consumer_goods_demand = 0.10

	industrial_efficiency = -0.10
	land_organisation = -0.50

#### Swedish Iron
Swedish_Iron_Narvik_Route = {

	potential = {
		tag = GER
		exists = SWE
		SWE = {
			not = { faction = comintern }
			not = { faction = allies }
		}
		not = {
			65 = { #Narvik
				controller = {
					faction = allies
				}
			}
		}
		not = {
			812 = { #Oslo
				controller = {
					faction = allies
				}
			}
		}
		or = {
			not = {
				war_with = ENG
				war_with = FRA
			}
			and = {
				65 = { #Narvik
					controller = {
						faction = axis
					}
				}
				812 = { #Oslo
					controller = {
						faction = axis
					}
				}
			}
		}
	}

	trigger = {
		has_country_flag = german_swedish_agreement
		not = { has_country_flag = german_swedish_agreement_stop }
	}

	global_money = -0.15
	global_metal = 0.30

	icon = 13
}

# MAGINOT-LINE OCCUPIED
maginot_occupied = {

	potential = {
		tag = FRA
		war_with = GER
		not =  {has_global_flag = NO_MODIFIERS }
		or = {
			not = { 2618 = { controlled_by = FRA } } #Metz
			not = { 2881 = { controlled_by = FRA } } #Strasbourg
			not = { 3150 = { controlled_by = FRA } } #Mulhouse
			not = { 3083 = { controlled_by = FRA } } #Colmar
			not = { 2750 = { controlled_by = FRA } } #Wissembourg
		}
		not = { exists = VIC }
		not = { year = 1941 }
		FRA = { government_in_exile = no }
		GER = { has_country_flag = fr_goal_nag }
	}

	trigger = {
		or = {
			not = { 2618 = { controlled_by = FRA } } #Metz
			not = { 2881 = { controlled_by = FRA } } #Strasbourg
			not = { 3150 = { controlled_by = FRA } } #Mulhouse
			not = { 3083 = { controlled_by = FRA } } #Colmar
			not = { 2750 = { controlled_by = FRA } } #Wissembourg
		}
	}

	national_unity = -20.00

	icon = 5
}

# Captain of industry
captain_of_industry = {

	potential = {

	}

	trigger = {
		check_variable = { which = aluminium_ActualBalance value = 1001 }
		or = {
			and = {
				check_variable = { which = tank_factory_count value = 20 }
				check_variable = { which = automotive_factory_count value = 20 }
			}
			and = {
				or = {
					check_variable = { which = tank_factory_count value = 25 }
					check_variable = { which = automotive_factory_count value = 25 }
				}
				check_variable = { which = BaseIC value = 500 }
			}
		}
        or = { ###########ballbearings
			or = {
				1171 = { controlled_by = this }
                1171 = { controller = { vassal_of = this } }
			}
            or = {
				2376 = { controlled_by = this }
				2376 = { controller = { vassal_of = this } }
			}
            any_owned_province = {
				and = {
					strategic_resource = ballbearings
                    controlled_by = this
				}
			}
            any_owned_province = {
				and = {
					strategic_resource = automotive_industry
                    controlled_by = this
				}
			}
        }
	}

	global_money = 0.35
	industrial_efficiency = 0.05

	icon = 42
}

# Island Hopping Bonus 1 - for 8 islands captured and held
island_effect_1 = {

	potential = {
		or = {
			tag = USA
			tag = JAP
		}
		this = { check_variable = { which = "islandsHopped" value = 8 } }
		not = { this = { check_variable = { which = "islandsHopped" value = 9 } } }
		USA = { war_with = JAP	}
	}

	trigger = {
		or = {
			tag = USA
			tag = JAP
		}
	}

	global_manpower_modifier = 0.01
	national_unity = 0.01
	global_ic = 0.01
	dissent = -0.01
	supply_throughput = 0.02

	icon = 24
}

omg_effect = {

	potential = {
		tag = OMG
	}

	#global_manpower_modifier = -1000.00
	global_ic = -1000.00
	global_money = -1000.00
	research_efficiency = -1000.00
	#officer_recruitment = -1000.00
	industrial_efficiency = -1000.00
	national_unity = 100
	neutrality_change = 1.00
	drift_speed = -1.00
	icon = 24
}

us_early_war_36 = {
	potential = {
		tag = USA
	}
	trigger = {
		has_country_flag = us_early_war
		year = 1936
		NOT = {
			year = 1937
		}
	}

	industrial_efficiency = 0.15
	air_build_speed = -0.15
	land_build_speed = -0.15
	naval_build_speed = -0.15
	tank_build_speed = -0.15

	icon = 38
}

Great_depression_effect = {

	potential = {
		tag = USA
		ai = no
	}

	trigger = {
		tag = USA
		ai = no
	}

	global_supplies = -0.275
	money = -0.1
	global_manpower_modifier = -0.15
	peace_consumer_goods_demand = 0.075
	war_consumer_goods_demand = 0.075
	industrial_efficiency = -0.05

	icon = 37
}

US_navy_buildup = {

	potential = {
		tag = USA
		war_with = JAP
		has_country_flag = naval_act_1938
		has_country_flag = two_ocean_navy_act
	}

	trigger = {
		tag = USA
		war_with = JAP
		has_country_flag = naval_act_1938
		has_country_flag = two_ocean_navy_act
	}

	naval_base_efficiency = 0.1
	naval_build_speed = -0.15
	land_build_speed = 0.05

	icon = 76
}

AI_Multiplayer_Bonus = {

	potential = {
		or = {
		GER = {has_country_flag = Multiplayer}
		USA = {has_country_flag = Multiplayer}
		SOV = {has_country_flag = Multiplayer}
		ENG = {has_country_flag = Multiplayer}
		}
		ai = yes

	}

	trigger = {
	}

		global_manpower_modifier = 0.85
		global_ic = 0.25
		naval_base_efficiency = 0.2
		industrial_efficiency = 0.25
		research_efficiency = 0.15
		supply_throughput = 0.25
		global_resources = 0.3
		global_energy = 0.35
		global_crude_oil = 0.15
		officer_recruitment = 1
		global_revolt_risk = -6
		global_money = 1.5
		air_intercept = 0.2
		global_leadership_modifier = 0.2
		national_unity = 0.1
		territorial_pride = 0.3
		repair_rate = 0.2

	icon = 4
}

Vichy_Bonus = {

	potential = {
		tag = GER
		exists = VIC
		or = {
		3484 = { controlled_by = VIC }
		4033 = { controlled_by = VIC }
		4229 = { controlled_by = VIC } }
		has_country_flag = fr_goal_nag
	}

	trigger = {
		VIC = {
				not = { alliance_with = GER }
				not = { alliance_with = ENG }
				is_in_any_faction = no
				is_subject = no
			}
	}

		global_manpower_modifier = 0.1
		global_leadership_modifier = 0.01

	icon = 12
}

		JAP = { faction = axis is_subject = no}
		HUN = { faction = axis is_subject = no}
		ROM = { faction = axis is_subject = no}

		faction = axis

		exists = FIN
		3778 = { controlled_by = ROM }
		or = {
			exists = CRO
			exists = SER
			exists = SLO
			and = {
				ai = yes
				3912 = { controller = { faction = axis } }
			}
		}
	}

	trigger = {
		GER = { faction = axis is_subject = no }
		ITA = { faction = axis is_subject = no }
		JAP = { faction = axis is_subject = no }
		HUN = { faction = axis is_subject = no }
		ROM = { faction = axis is_subject = no }
		FIN = { faction = axis is_subject = no }

		CRO = { faction = axis }

		SLO = { faction = axis } }

lack_of_strat_resource_ship_armor_techs = {

	potential = {
		or = {
			and = {
				Vickers_steel = 1
				not = { check_variable = { which = copper_ActualBalance value = 1000 } }
			}
			and = {
				Cemented_armor  = 1
				not = { check_variable = { which = manganese_ActualBalance value = 1000 } }
				not = { check_variable = { which = chromite_ActualBalance value = 1000 } }
			}
			and = {
				Special_treatment_steel  = 1
				not = { check_variable = { which = nickel_ActualBalance value = 1000 } }
				not = { check_variable = { which = chromite_ActualBalance value = 1000 } }
			}
		}
	}

	trigger = {
		has_country_flag = strat_resource_system_normal
		or = {
			and = {
				Vickers_steel = 1
				not = { check_variable = { which = copper_ActualBalance value = 1000 } }
			}
			and = {
				Cemented_armor  = 1
				not = { check_variable = { which = manganese_ActualBalance value = 1000 } }
				not = { check_variable = { which = chromite_ActualBalance value = 1000 } }
			}
			and = {
				Special_treatment_steel  = 1
				not = { check_variable = { which = nickel_ActualBalance value = 1000 } }
				not = { check_variable = { which = chromite_ActualBalance value = 1000 } }
			}
		}
	}

	naval_build_speed = 0.05

	icon = 50
}

lack_of_money_strategic_effect = {
	potential = {
		ai = no
		check_variable = {
			which = "BaseIC"
			value = 150
		}
	}
	trigger = {
		check_variable = {
			which = "BaseIC"
			value = 150
		}
		has_country_flag = budget_over_2000
		not = {
			money = 3000
		}
		date = 1936.7.1
	}

	icon = 41
}

		}

		}

		}

genrikh_lyushkov_defection = {
	potential = {
		tag = JAP
		has_country_flag = genrikh_lyushkov_defection_yes
		not = { year = 1941 } #Intel only useful for some time
		war_with = SOV
	}
	trigger = {
		tag = JAP
		has_country_flag = genrikh_lyushkov_defection_yes
		not = { year = 1941 } #Intel only useful for some time
		war_with = SOV
	}

	land_organisation = 0.05

	icon = 5
}

########## SMALL SHIPYARDS COUNT #######################################################

triggered_mod_small_shipyard_core_1 = {
	potential = {
		check_variable = { which = "small_ship_shipyard_count" value = 1 }
		not = { check_variable = { which = "small_ship_shipyard_count" value = 2 } }
	}
	trigger = {
		check_variable = { which = "small_ship_shipyard_count" value = 1 }
		not = { check_variable = { which = "small_ship_shipyard_count" value = 2 } }
	}

	icon = 50
}
triggered_mod_small_shipyard_core_2 = {
	potential = {
		check_variable = { which = "small_ship_shipyard_count" value = 2 }
		not = { check_variable = { which = "small_ship_shipyard_count" value = 3 } }

	trigger = {

		not = { check_variable = { which = "small_ship_shipyard_count" value = 3 } }
	}

		check_variable = { which = "medium_ship_shipyard_count" value = 74 }
		not = { check_variable = { which = "medium_ship_shipyard_count" value = 75 } }
	}
	trigger = {
		check_variable = { which = "medium_ship_shipyard_count" value = 74 }
		not = { check_variable = { which = "medium_ship_shipyard_count" value = 75 } }
	}

	icon = 50
}

		check_variable = { which = "heavy_aircraft_factory_count" value = 33 }
		not = { check_variable = { which = "heavy_aircraft_factory_count" value = 34 } }
	}
	trigger = {
		check_variable = { which = "heavy_aircraft_factory_count" value = 33 }
		not = { check_variable = { which = "heavy_aircraft_factory_count" value = 34 } }
	}
	#air_build_speed = -0.165
	icon = 49
}

		not = { check_variable = { which = "research_lab_count" value = 2 } }

triggered_mod_hospital_core_1 = {
	potential = {
		check_variable = { which = "hospital_count" value = 1 }
		not = { check_variable = { which = "hospital_count" value = 2 } }
	}
	trigger = {
		check_variable = { which = "hospital_count" value = 1 }
		not = { check_variable = { which = "hospital_count" value = 2 } }
	}
	casualty_trickleback = 0.01
	icon = 47

########## RAIL TERMINUS COUNT #######################################################

triggered_mod_rail_terminous_core_1 = {
	potential = {
		check_variable = { which = "rail_terminous_count" value = 1 }
		not = { check_variable = { which = "rail_terminous_count" value = 2 } }
	}
	trigger = {
		check_variable = { which = "rail_terminous_count" value = 1 }
		not = { check_variable = { which = "rail_terminous_count" value = 2 } }
	}
	#casualty_trickleback = 0.02
	icon = 30
}

	potential = {
		check_variable = { which = "rail_terminous_count" value = 99 }
		not = { check_variable = { which = "rail_terminous_count" value = 100 } }
	}
	trigger = {
		check_variable = { which = "rail_terminous_count" value = 99 }
		not = { check_variable = { which = "rail_terminous_count" value = 100 } }
	}
	#naval_build_speed = -0.24
	icon = 50
}

FRA_AI_CG_FIX = {
	potential = {
		ai = yes
		tag = FRA
	}
	trigger = {
		ai = yes
		tag = FRA
		GER = { ai = no }
	}
	peace_consumer_goods_demand = -1
	war_consumer_goods_demand = -1
	icon = 50
}
FRA_AI_CG_FIX_AI_GER = {
	potential = {
		ai = yes
		tag = FRA
	}
	trigger = {
		ai = yes
		tag = FRA
		GER = { ai = yes }
	}
	peace_consumer_goods_demand = -0.50
	war_consumer_goods_demand = -0.50
	icon = 50
}

Late_War_Europe_AI_supply_fix = {
	potential = {
		ai = yes
		year = 1945
		or = {
			tag = SOV
			tag = USA
		}
	}
	trigger = {
		ai = yes
		year = 1945
		exists = GER
		or = {
			tag = SOV
			tag = USA
		}
	}

veteran_expertise_1 = {
	potential = {
		check_variable = { which = "veteran_expertise" value = 1 }
		not = { check_variable = { which = "veteran_expertise" value = 2 } }
	}
	trigger = {
		check_variable = { which = "veteran_expertise" value = 1 }
		not = { check_variable = { which = "veteran_expertise" value = 2 } }
	}
	unit_start_experience = 0.5
	icon = 60
}
